{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hi there."},{"time":2000,"text":"I'm going to be talking a little bit about"},{"time":4000,"text":"music, machines and life."},{"time":7000,"text":"Or, more specifically,"},{"time":10000,"text":"what we learned from the creation of a very large and complicated machine"},{"time":13000,"text":"for a music video."},{"time":15000,"text":"Some of you may recognize this image."},{"time":17000,"text":"This is the opening frame of the video that we created."},{"time":20000,"text":"We'll be showing the video at the end,"},{"time":22000,"text":"but before we do, I want to talk a little bit about"},{"time":25000,"text":"what it is that they wanted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"Now, when we first started talking to OK Go --"},{"time":30000,"text":"the name of the song is \"This Too Shall Pass\" --"},{"time":33000,"text":"we were really excited because"},{"time":35000,"text":"they expressed interest in building a machine that they could dance with."},{"time":38000,"text":"And we were very excited about this"},{"time":40000,"text":"because, of course,"},{"time":42000,"text":"they have a history of dancing with machines."},{"time":45000,"text":"They're responsible for this video, \"Here It Goes Again.\""},{"time":48000,"text":"50-million-plus views on YouTube."},{"time":50000,"text":"Four guys dancing on treadmills,"},{"time":53000,"text":"no cuts, just a static camera."},{"time":55000,"text":"A fantastically viral and wonderful video."},{"time":57000,"text":"So we were really excited about working with them."},{"time":59000,"text":"And we sort of started talking about what it is that they wanted."},{"time":62000,"text":"And they explained that they wanted"},{"time":64000,"text":"kind of a Rube Goldberg machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"Now, for those of you who don't know,"},{"time":69000,"text":"a Rube Goldberg machine"},{"time":71000,"text":"is a complicated contraption,"},{"time":73000,"text":"an incredibly over-engineered piece of machinery"},{"time":76000,"text":"that accomplishes a relatively simple task."},{"time":79000,"text":"So we were excited by this idea,"},{"time":81000,"text":"and we started talking about"},{"time":83000,"text":"exactly what it would look like."},{"time":85000,"text":"And we came up with some parameters, because,"},{"time":87000,"text":"you know, building a Rube Goldberg machine"},{"time":89000,"text":"has limitations,"},{"time":92000,"text":"but it also is pretty wide open."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"And we wanted to make sure that we did something"},{"time":97000,"text":"that would work for a music video."},{"time":100000,"text":"So we came up with a list of requirements,"},{"time":103000,"text":"the \"10 commandments,\""},{"time":105000,"text":"and they were, in order of ascending difficulty:"},{"time":108000,"text":"The first is \"No magic.\""},{"time":110000,"text":"Everything that happened on screen had to be"},{"time":112000,"text":"very easily understood by a typical viewer."},{"time":114000,"text":"The rule of thumb was that, if my mother couldn't understand it,"},{"time":117000,"text":"then we couldn't use it in the video."},{"time":119000,"text":"They wanted band integration,"},{"time":121000,"text":"that is, the machine acting upon the band members,"},{"time":124000,"text":"specifically not the other way around."},{"time":126000,"text":"They wanted the machine action to follow the song feeling."},{"time":129000,"text":"So as the song picks up emotion,"},{"time":131000,"text":"so should the machine"},{"time":133000,"text":"get grander in its process."},{"time":135000,"text":"They wanted us to make use of the space."},{"time":137000,"text":"So we have this 10,000-square-foot warehouse we were using,"},{"time":140000,"text":"divided between two floors."},{"time":142000,"text":"It included an exterior loading dock."},{"time":144000,"text":"We used all of that, including a giant hole in the floor"},{"time":147000,"text":"that we actually descended the camera and cameraman through."},{"time":150000,"text":"They wanted it messy, and we were happy to oblige."},{"time":153000,"text":"The machine itself would start the music."},{"time":155000,"text":"So the machine would get started,"},{"time":157000,"text":"it would travel some distance,"},{"time":159000,"text":"reacting along the way,"},{"time":161000,"text":"hit play on an iPod or a tape deck"},{"time":163000,"text":"or something that would start playback."},{"time":165000,"text":"And the machine would maintain synchronization throughout."},{"time":168000,"text":"And speaking of synchronization,"},{"time":170000,"text":"they wanted it to sync to the rhythm"},{"time":172000,"text":"and to hit specific beats along the way."},{"time":176000,"text":"Okay. (Laughter)"},{"time":179000,"text":"They wanted it to end precisely on time."},{"time":182000,"text":"Okay, so now the start to finish timing has to be perfect."},{"time":185000,"text":"And they wanted the music to drop out"},{"time":187000,"text":"at a certain point in the video"},{"time":189000,"text":"and actual live audio from the machine"},{"time":191000,"text":"to play part of the song."},{"time":194000,"text":"And as if that wasn't enough,"},{"time":196000,"text":"all of these incredibly complicating things, right,"},{"time":199000,"text":"they wanted it in one shot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208000,"text":"Okay."},{"time":211000,"text":"So, just some statistics"},{"time":213000,"text":"about what we went through in the process."},{"time":215000,"text":"The machine itself has"},{"time":217000,"text":"89 distinct interactions."},{"time":219000,"text":"It took us 85 takes"},{"time":222000,"text":"to get it on film"},{"time":224000,"text":"to our satisfaction."},{"time":226000,"text":"Of those 85 takes,"},{"time":228000,"text":"only three actually successfully completed their run."},{"time":232000,"text":"We destroyed two pianos"},{"time":234000,"text":"and 10 televisions in the process."},{"time":237000,"text":"We went to Home Depot well over a hundred times."},{"time":240000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":242000,"text":"And we lost one high-heeled shoe"},{"time":245000,"text":"when one of our engineers, Heather Knight,"},{"time":247000,"text":"left her high-heeled shoe -- after a nice dinner,"},{"time":249000,"text":"and returned back to the build --"},{"time":251000,"text":"and left it in a pile of stuff."},{"time":253000,"text":"And another engineer thought, \"Well, that would be a really good thing to use\""},{"time":255000,"text":"and ended up using it as a really nice trigger."},{"time":257000,"text":"And it's actually in the machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"So what did we learn from all of this?"},{"time":262000,"text":"Well, having completed this,"},{"time":264000,"text":"we have the opportunity to step back and reflect"},{"time":266000,"text":"on some of the things."},{"time":268000,"text":"And we learned that small stuff stinks."},{"time":270000,"text":"Little balls in wooden tracks"},{"time":273000,"text":"are really susceptible to"},{"time":275000,"text":"humidity and temperature and a little bit of dust,"},{"time":277000,"text":"and they fall out of the tracks,"},{"time":279000,"text":"the exact angles makes it hard to get right."},{"time":281000,"text":"And yet, a bowling ball will always follow the same path."},{"time":284000,"text":"It doesn't matter what temperature it is,"},{"time":286000,"text":"doesn't matter what's in its way;"},{"time":288000,"text":"it will pretty much get where it needs to go."},{"time":290000,"text":"But as much as the small stuff stinks, we needed somewhere to start,"},{"time":292000,"text":"so that we would have somewhere to go."},{"time":294000,"text":"And so you have to start with it. You have to focus on it."},{"time":297000,"text":"Small stuff stinks,"},{"time":299000,"text":"but, of course, it's essential, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"What else? Planning is incredibly important."},{"time":304000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":308000,"text":"You know, we spent a lot of time ideating"},{"time":310000,"text":"and even building some of these things."},{"time":312000,"text":"It's been said that, \"No battle plan"},{"time":314000,"text":"survives contact with the enemy.\""},{"time":316000,"text":"I think our enemy was physics --"},{"time":318000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":320000,"text":"and she's a cruel mistress."},{"time":323000,"text":"Often, we had to pull things out as a result"},{"time":325000,"text":"because of timing or aesthetics or whatever."},{"time":328000,"text":"And so while planning is important, so is flexibility."},{"time":331000,"text":"These are all things that ended up"},{"time":333000,"text":"not making it into the final machine."},{"time":335000,"text":"So also, put reliable stuff last,"},{"time":339000,"text":"the stuff that's going to run every time."},{"time":341000,"text":"Again, small to large is relevant here."},{"time":344000,"text":"The little Lego car in the beginning of the video"},{"time":347000,"text":"references the big, real car"},{"time":349000,"text":"near the end of the video."},{"time":351000,"text":"The big, real car works every time; there's no problem about it."},{"time":354000,"text":"The little one had a tendency to try to run off the track"},{"time":356000,"text":"and that's a problem."},{"time":358000,"text":"But you don't want to have to reset the whole machine"},{"time":360000,"text":"because the Lego car at the end doesn't work, right."},{"time":362000,"text":"So you put that up front so that, if it fails,"},{"time":364000,"text":"at least you know"},{"time":366000,"text":"you don't have to reset the whole thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"Life can be"},{"time":371000,"text":"messy."},{"time":374000,"text":"There were incredibly difficult moments in the building of this thing."},{"time":377000,"text":"Months were spent in this tiny, cold warehouse."},{"time":380000,"text":"And the wonderful elation that we had"},{"time":382000,"text":"when we finally completed it."},{"time":384000,"text":"So it's important to remember that whether it's good or it's bad,"},{"time":387000,"text":"\"This Too Shall Pass.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":397000,"text":"And now to introduce"}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"their music video,"},{"time":401000,"text":"we have OK Go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"OK Go: An introduction. Hello TEDxUSC."},{"time":405000,"text":"We are OK Go."},{"time":407000,"text":"What are we doing? Oh, just hanging out with our Grammy. What what!"},{"time":410000,"text":"It think we can do better than this. Hello TEDxUSC."},{"time":413000,"text":"We are OK Go. Have you read the \"Natural Curiosity Cabinet?\""},{"time":416000,"text":"I mean, \"Curiosity\" -- excuse me."},{"time":418000,"text":"Let me start again."},{"time":420000,"text":"We need some more ridiculous things besides \"The Cabinet of Natural Curiosities.\""},{"time":423000,"text":"Tim's sundial hat."},{"time":425000,"text":"Have you seen the new work they've done to the Waltz Towers?"},{"time":427000,"text":"Sorry, start again."},{"time":429000,"text":"(Barking)"},{"time":431000,"text":"Dogs."},{"time":433000,"text":"Hello, TEDxUSC. We are OK Go,"},{"time":435000,"text":"and this our new video, \"This Too Shall Pass.\""},{"time":438000,"text":"[unclear]"},{"time":440000,"text":"Kay, we can still do one better I think, yeah."},{"time":443000,"text":"That one's pretty good. It's getting better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":486000,"text":"♫ You know you can't keep letting it get you down ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":489000,"text":"♫ And you can't keep dragging that dead weight around ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"♫ If there ain't all that much to lug around ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":501000,"text":"♫ Better run like hell when you hit the ground ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":521000,"text":"♫ You can't stop these kids from dancing ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":524000,"text":"♫ Why would you want to? ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"♫ Especially when you're already getting yours ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"♫ Cuz if your mind don't move and your knees don't bend ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"♫ Well don't go blaming the kids again ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":556000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":565000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"♫ Let it go ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"♫ This too shall pass ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"♫ Let it go ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":595000,"text":"♫ This too shall pass ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"♫ You know you can't keep letting it get you down ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"♫ No, you can't keep letting it get you down ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":615000,"text":"♫ Let it go ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"♫ This too shall pass ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649000,"text":"♫ When the morning comes ♫"}]},{"cues":[{"time":658000,"text":"(Cheering)"}]}]}